# Whitelist, not blacklist: `main` ignores EVERYTHING by default and only tracks
# the libseq tooling listed below. Graph folders are independent clones of the
# graphs/* branches (each with its own real .git dir); main records nothing about
# them, so the folders just stay ignored here.
#
# `/*` is anchored and top-level only, so un-ignoring a directory below is enough
# to track all of its contents.
/*

# ...except the tooling that lives on main:
!/.gitattributes
!/.gitignore
!/.libexclude
!/README.md
!/LICENSE
!/libseq.bat
!/sys/
